lead_paragraph: Former Secretary of State of State Hillary Rodham Clinton urged North Carolina Democrats on Saturday to work to re-elect Sen. Kay Hagan, stumping for the incumbent in a race that will help decide which party controls the U.S. Senate.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Rallies NC Democrats for Sen Hagan
headline.print_headline: Hillary Clinton Rallies NC Democrats for Sen Hagan
